des:
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo. 

After connecting Alexa to your VIZO Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "VIZO" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one VIZO account in our "VIZO" app;
(3). You need to have some VIZO smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our VIZO" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "VIZO Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "VIZO Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "VIZO Smart", and you'll be navigated to VIZO login page;
(9). Input your VIZO account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"

Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch,
smart socket, 
smart bulb....
